00:47:42,067 --> 00:47:44,820
It's your fucking fault we'll all die!

531
00:47:56,915 --> 00:47:58,375
I'll look for the item.

532
00:47:59,418 --> 00:48:00,752
It's too late now.

533
00:48:01,795 --> 00:48:03,547
Maybe this is just to please myself,

534
00:48:05,757 --> 00:48:06,675
but…

535
00:48:10,554 --> 00:48:11,722
I want to do everything I can

536
00:48:13,390 --> 00:48:14,891
to the very end.

537
00:48:26,528 --> 00:48:27,738
She sure is tough.

538
00:48:30,157 --> 00:48:31,575
I could never do that.

539
00:49:07,611 --> 00:49:10,197
All that crap about cooperating
was such bullshit.

540
00:49:14,034 --> 00:49:15,911
Fucking self-righteous bastards.

541
00:49:18,580 --> 00:49:19,498
Fuck it all!

542
00:49:31,093 --> 00:49:32,678
I was such a fool.

543
00:49:44,272 --> 00:49:48,193
I don't have much time anyway.

544
00:50:41,496 --> 00:50:42,664
There must be…

545
00:50:43,165 --> 00:50:44,666
There must be a way.

546
00:50:59,806 --> 00:51:00,849
I found it!

547
00:51:11,902 --> 00:51:14,988
The Player Team obtained an item.

548
00:51:17,532 --> 00:51:20,452
The King of Clubs Team
leads by 500 points.

549
00:51:22,120 --> 00:51:23,830
Usagi got the item.

550
00:51:26,792 --> 00:51:28,126
Only 500 more points.

551
00:51:29,252 --> 00:51:30,295
I've got to do something.

552
00:51:31,171 --> 00:51:32,380
I've got to do something!

553
00:51:35,884 --> 00:51:37,677
I'll go to Kyuma's base.

554
00:51:37,761 --> 00:51:38,595
Why?

555
00:51:39,095 --> 00:51:42,098
We just need 500 points.
Some kind of miracle could happen!

556
00:51:43,099 --> 00:51:44,142
That's ridiculous.

557
00:51:44,226 --> 00:51:47,562
If I'm going to die anyway,
I want to do everything I can before I do!

558
00:51:48,438 --> 00:51:49,481
Arisu…

559
00:51:54,027 --> 00:51:57,280
Come to think of it, I never did tell you.

560
00:52:00,534 --> 00:52:01,576
Tatta…

561
00:52:03,286 --> 00:52:07,541
You've always been so optimistic.
You've really cheered me up.

562
00:52:12,420 --> 00:52:13,463
Thank you.

563
00:52:26,893 --> 00:52:29,145
Time remaining, ten minutes.

564
00:52:29,229 --> 00:52:32,315
The King of Clubs Team
leads by 500 points.

565
00:52:32,399 --> 00:52:33,316
We can still win.

566
00:52:42,367 --> 00:52:43,201
Niragi?

567
00:52:54,462 --> 00:52:56,047
Pretty pitiful, huh?

568
00:52:57,215 --> 00:52:58,800
I found the item!

569
00:52:58,884 --> 00:53:00,218
We just need 500 more points!

570
00:53:00,302 --> 00:53:01,511
Don't be stupid.

571
00:53:02,762 --> 00:53:04,264
I'm not giving up.

572
00:53:11,021 --> 00:53:12,439
We're going to die.

573
00:53:13,481 --> 00:53:15,150
Both you and I are going to die.

574
00:53:17,652 --> 00:53:19,571
I've got no hope left.

575
00:53:25,493 --> 00:53:27,078
You people…

576
00:53:27,704 --> 00:53:30,832
you've always got
a righteous look on your faces.

577
00:53:35,754 --> 00:53:37,505
Do I really disgust you that much?

578
00:53:38,548 --> 00:53:39,424
Do I?

579
00:53:41,259 --> 00:53:43,762
Everyone looks at me that way.

580
00:53:53,188 --> 00:53:56,942
I don't know if everyone hated me
because I was twisted,

581
00:53:58,526 --> 00:54:02,530
or if I became twisted
because everyone hated me.

582
00:54:06,159 --> 00:54:07,702
Remember what Kyuma said?

583
00:54:09,955 --> 00:54:12,874
We can see a person's true character
in the face of death.

584
00:54:15,752 --> 00:54:16,836
I finally understand

585
00:54:17,629 --> 00:54:18,880
after facing death.

586
00:54:20,715 --> 00:54:23,468
I'm not like you people
who take the blame for others.

587
00:54:25,261 --> 00:54:28,181
I'm not the kind of person
who clings to hopes and dreams.

588
00:54:30,642 --> 00:54:31,726
I'm scum.

589
00:54:56,584 --> 00:54:59,421
I can finally pick up where we left off.

590
00:55:01,297 --> 00:55:02,882
Let's have a good fuck

591
00:55:02,966 --> 00:55:05,969
and face the end of our lives
with a smile on our faces!

592
00:55:15,020 --> 00:55:16,104
Usagi!

593
00:55:20,150 --> 00:55:21,067
Arisu!

594
00:55:22,068 --> 00:55:23,069
Shut up!

595
00:55:37,500 --> 00:55:39,586
Time remaining, nine minutes.

596
00:55:40,128 --> 00:55:43,173
The King of Clubs Team
leads by 500 points.

597
